Technology stack

Source control:
	Git
	GitHub

Backend programming language:
	Python 2.7

Web framework:
	Python Flask

Database:
	PostgreSQL
	sqlalchemy (lets us write python to database)

Templating language:
	Jinja - Built into Flask

Front end styling:
	Twitter Bootstrap
	CSS / LESS

Deployment:
	Web-server: ngnix
	Web Server Gateway Interface (WSGI) server: gunicorn 
	
Hardware:
	Database server
	Web server (API)
	Wab server (frontend)

Dev and server environment:
	Ubuntu linux

Python Plugins
	sqlalchemy
	psycopg2
	Sijax
	wtforms
	requests

Flask Plugins
	Flask-security - login
	Flask-social - facebook, twitter, google login
	Flask-mail
	Flask-SQLAlchemy
	Flask-migrate
	Flask-script
	Flask-sijax
	Flask-wtf
	Flask-HTMLmin - Will minify website, for both security and optimization
    Flask-Babel - translation toolkit